title: PPPP’s Makhdoom Mehboob Zaman wins PS- 56 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP) Makhdoom Mehboob Zaman has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-56, Matiari-I, by securing 72,178 votes.
According to unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Naseer Ahmed, Pakistan Muslim League (Nawaz), who bagged vote 35,432.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 54.77 %.
